Author: notabel
Content: Do we have any metrics on liveness of accounts?  I've certainly felt that the community of active, thoughtful commentators is pretty small (not a bad thing!).

Author: danielha
Content:
It's that time of the year again. Don't forget to register by this Monday if you plan on going -- you save $200. Students also get 65% off the workshop package (use coupon code: webex07ftst at registration).

My co-founder, Jason, and I plan on attending. It'll be our first Web2.0 expo. Is anyone else planning to attend? Any veterans care to share their past experiences?

Author: danielha
Title: Web 2.0 Expo 2007, April 15-18, 2007, San Francisco, California

Author: pg
Content: Oddly enough I'd never checked before, but as of now there are 1426 accounts. The reddits told me once that about 1 out of 10 visitors there is logged in, so this seems about right.
